WEBVTT

00:03.836 --> 00:06.157
To discuss taking the firm
international. I want you there.

00:08.642 --> 00:12.144
Shane, the statement that you gave the
police, it doesn't line up with Taylor's.

00:12.146 --> 00:14.546
You saw the girl
who was staying at the motel?

00:14.615 --> 00:16.648
Yeah, but not Taylor.

00:16.684 --> 00:18.984
It was another girl
that was staying there.

00:19.119 --> 00:22.287
- Meet your new cellmate.
- You got the top bunk.

00:24.258 --> 00:27.326
I know, it's a lot to process.

00:27.461 --> 00:29.261
Tim wants to get
Shane's testimony

00:29.263 --> 00:32.264
as soon as possible.
Shane's not well.

00:34.201 --> 00:36.535
- Nice out here?
- Sorry?

00:36.604 --> 00:38.470
Don't you think it's beautiful?

00:38.605 --> 00:40.739
I suppose if you can
get over the creepy.

00:40.808 --> 00:43.141
I guess I don't
see it as creepy.

00:43.177 --> 00:45.544
Remember when we came
here for Halloween?

00:45.613 --> 00:47.780
That was creepy though.

00:49.417 --> 00:51.216
We're here.

00:51.351 --> 00:53.619
I...

00:53.754 --> 00:56.822
I found this while I was
walking the dog.

00:56.891 --> 00:58.891
I thought you might
want to see it.

00:58.893 --> 01:01.093
- You just happened to pass by?
- Yeah,

01:01.162 --> 01:04.663
after a quick...
database search.

01:06.366 --> 01:07.899
Looks like
the Hanleys have been here

01:07.968 --> 01:09.901
a while.

01:09.937 --> 01:12.104
My grandparents.
I was working with my dad

01:12.173 --> 01:14.806
on the Oswalt Power
and Coal Harbour Energy merger

01:14.875 --> 01:17.843
in Toronto. He didn't even
come to the funeral.

01:17.912 --> 01:20.111
He just bought this.

01:20.147 --> 01:23.782
"Survived by their loving son
David Richard Hanley."

01:23.917 --> 01:25.850
Of course he'd put his name
on their grave.

01:25.886 --> 01:28.653
- In a really big font.
- Yeah.

01:28.722 --> 01:31.523
It's nice here.

01:31.592 --> 01:35.394
Not a bad place to be buried.

01:35.529 --> 01:37.395
Yeah, it is.

01:37.465 --> 01:39.498
It's far too nice for him.

01:43.370 --> 01:45.871
Let me get to the point.
Is a settlement

01:45.940 --> 01:48.006
out of the question?
We had offered

01:48.075 --> 01:51.343
the defense a more than generous settlement,
which, I'm sure you can remember,

01:51.412 --> 01:54.045
they decided to turn into
a public stunt, consequently

01:54.115 --> 01:57.015
wasting the court's time. I'm
sure Mr. Bennett would agree

01:57.084 --> 01:59.151
that forcing
an innocent young woman

01:59.286 --> 02:01.086
to four years of prison
hardly qualifies

02:01.221 --> 02:03.155
as a settlement offer
and perhaps

02:03.290 --> 02:05.224
alternatively, a threat.

02:05.226 --> 02:07.492
Save it for trial,
Ms. Chan. Has anything else

02:07.528 --> 02:10.961
magically materialized
since then?

02:11.031 --> 02:14.233
We'd be willing
to entertain a settlement

02:14.235 --> 02:17.102
if it included
a full withdrawal of charges.

02:17.104 --> 02:18.971
I bet you would.

02:19.106 --> 02:22.374
A simple "no" would have
sufficed. Alright,

02:22.509 --> 02:25.377
are we in agreement
that we are trying

02:25.512 --> 02:28.880
the murder
of David Richard Hanley?

02:28.916 --> 02:31.716
- Yes, Your Honour.
- Ms. Chan, are we in agreement

02:31.785 --> 02:33.718
that the victim was murdered?

02:33.754 --> 02:35.720
Yes, Your Honour.

02:35.756 --> 02:38.857
We won't be pursuing
a strategy of self-defense.

02:38.992 --> 02:41.860
And that the murder weapon was the
bottle found at the crime scene?

02:45.032 --> 02:48.934
Was the blow to the anterior
base of the skull? Yes?

02:49.003 --> 02:51.603
Alright, are there
any other witnesses to add

02:51.639 --> 02:53.605
to the slate?
I'd like to do that now.

02:53.641 --> 02:55.874
No surprises.

02:55.943 --> 02:59.911
- Not from us, Your Honour.
- No, Your Honour.

02:59.947 --> 03:02.780
I expect you both
to be efficient,

03:02.816 --> 03:06.084
respectful and to play
by the rules.

03:06.153 --> 03:08.219
If there's anything else
either of you wants to say,

03:08.255 --> 03:10.155
now is the time.

03:14.962 --> 03:18.130
Good luck, Counsellors.
There's no turning back now.

